com.thedemgel.regions.feature

Class Feature

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thedemgel.regions.feature.Feature

  • public class Feature
extends Object
    Features are executed from WorldRegionEvent, either onTick or based on Events. Features are attached to a FeatureHolder, and FeatureHolders are attached to RAZs (in the case of parent FeatureHolders, they are attached to many RAZs.
